<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c1">"أحد الثقات الأثبات"</span>. <span class="c1">"الفتح"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٩٦)</span>. <span class="c1">"ثقة مشهور"</span>. <span class="c1">"الفتح"</span> <span class="c2">(٨/ ٧٢٤)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
